      "description": "Presented in exemplary, concours-level condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior, has been meticulously maintained to satisfy the most discerning collector. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically uncompromising, this specimen offers a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state. We invite serious inquiries to inspect a machine that stands as a testament to rigorous care and uncompromising standards.",
