    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely pristine! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and honestly still has that fresh new-car smell. The paint is flawless and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
