      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, and it still has that fresh new-car smell. It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept its whole life, and it runs like an absolute dream. I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
