      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1997 Acura NSX-T is a superlative example of mid-engine engineering, featuring the 3.2L C32B VTEC V6 mated to the desirable 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission. The factory-original aluminum monocoque remains structurally pristine, preserving the razor-sharp turn-in and neutral handling characteristics afforded by its double-wishbone suspension and recalibrated spring rates. This specimen retains its original VIN-matched body panels and factory-correct finish, showing zero signs of mechanical fatigue or thermal degradation in the engine bay. A true collector-grade vehicle, it offers an unadulterated analog driving experience with perfect synchro engagement and a linear power delivery that remains benchmark-standard.",
